804  }
805  init_result = scope.Yield(*init_result);
806  } else {

815  t->ToString() + " originally defined at " +
816  PositionAsString(stmt->pos),
817  t)});
818  }
819  init_result =
820  VisitResult(*type, assembler().TopRange(lowered_types.size()));

823  ? LocationReference::Temporary(
824  *init_result, "const " + stmt->name->value)
